who": "David Boder", "start": "2122.514","u": "Hm . . ."},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2122.755","u": "Those were the so-called counter-revolutionary trials."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2126.183","u": "Yes . . ."},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2126.978","u": "And I was established as a lawyer in spite of the fact that I took part in the so-called counter-revolutionary trials . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2135.231","u": "You defended them?"},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2136.225","u": ". . . I defended [them]. The government&#226;the Soviet government&#226;gives anyone who is indicted [and] that is already provided for in the Constitution, the right to have a defender [a lawyer, legal council]. He has a right to choose council; and if he has no council the government provides one. And so it happened often, that I had a chance to represent such [people] in counter-revolutionary trials; and I must affirm that they had all the rights of defense just like in any other country."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2171.324","u": "Did you ever win [such] a case?"},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2173.113","u": "There were cases when there were indicted citizens&#226;Soviet citizens, also Polish citizens -for counter-revolutionary agitation and propaganda. And as a consequence [in course of] the trial, it was often revealed that the testimonies of the witnesses were not correct and there were often cases that the people were set free."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2197.365","u": "That was not a military court?"},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2199.715","u": "No. Such special general courts which handled all other cases; and they also decide the cases of the counter-revolutionary activities."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2210.028","u": "Did they have a jury? [Repeats the term in Russian]."},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2213.131","u": "There in Russia it is arranged that there is a president [presiding judge] who is elected, and in addition there are peoples&#39; representatives."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2223.120","u": "How many?"},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2223.994","u": "Two."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2225.018","u": "And they handle [?] the trial?"},    {"who": "Jacob Wilf", "start": "2228.602","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2230.168","u": "Thank you very much, Mr. Wilf. This was a special report&#226;a special message [Wire apparently terminates in the middle of the sentence]."}        ]
    }
_jsready = true;
var return_val;
switch (String(type)){
        case "transcription":
        return_val = transcription.interview;
        break;
            case "english_translation":
        return_val = english_translation.interview;
        break;
    }
return return_val;
}
function js_ready(){
    return _jsready;
}
